		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Tilt</td>\r\n			<td>-5 to +25&deg;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Warranty Information</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Manufacturing Warranty</td>\r\n			<td>3 year</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>HP V20 19.5&quot; HD+ LED TN Monitor</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The HP V20 19.5&quot; HD+ LED TN Monitor is the quintessential, everyday monitor that adjusts to your needs, saves space, and doesn&rsquo;t break the bank. Get lifelike color and sharp details on a 19.5&rdquo; diagonal HD+ (1600 x 900 pixel) screen. You can tilt the screen up to 5&deg; forward or 25&deg; backward to find your best viewing position. You have the freedom to connect devices and other monitors quickly through HDMI and VGA ports. Enjoy greater eye comfort as the Low Blue Light feature reduces whites and makes colors warmer. Experience better response times and higher refresh rates with the addition of the twisted nematic LED display. Environmentally conscious features include ENERGY STAR Certified and mercury-free LED display backlighting. It has 3 years warranty.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What is the price of HP V20 19.5&quot; HD+ Monitor in Bangladesh?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The latest price of HP V20 19.5&quot; HD+ Monitor in Bangladesh is 8,800৳. You can buy the HP V20 19.5&quot; HD+ Monitor at best price from our website or visit any of our showrooms.</p>', 'product-image/HP V20 19.5 HD+ LED TN Monitor.jpg', 1, '2021-06-16 10:13:39', '2021-06-16 10:13:39'),
